<!--
    Plane marker, pointing north (up) at rotate=0.
    Visual center is aligned to the drawable center (28, 28) so the icon
    rotates cleanly in place instead of swinging through an arc.
    Bbox: x [2, 54], y [3, 53].  Midpoint = (28, 28). ✓
-->
